origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "MortgageRate.get",
        "description": "获取当前的抵押贷款利率",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "rates",
                "description": "返回当前的抵押贷款利率"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "FinancialAnalysis.analyze",
        "description": "分析月度支付数据以评估财务影响",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "monthly_payments",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "月度支付数据的列表"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "impact",
                "description": "返回财务影响的分析结果"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "PortfolioOptimization.optimize",
        "description": "优化投资组合以最大化回报并最小化风险",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "assets",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "投资组合中的资产列表"
            },
            {
                "name": "expected_returns",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "每个资产的预期回报率"
            },
            {
                "name": "covariance_matrix",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "资产之间的协方差矩阵"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "optimized_weights",
                "description": "返回优化后的资产权重"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "CostReduction.strategies",
        "description": "获取成本削减策略的建议",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "strategies",
                "description": "返回成本削减策略的建议"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "MortgageCalculator.calculate",
        "description": "计算抵押贷款的月度还款额",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "principal",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "贷款本金"
            },
            {
                "name": "rate",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "年利率"
            },
            {
                "name": "term",
                "type": "INTEGER",
                "description": "贷款期限（以月为单位）"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "monthly_payment",
                "description": "返回月度还款额"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "RiskAssessment.evaluate",
        "description": "评估投资组合的风险水平",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "portfolio_value",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "投资组合的总价值"
            },
            {
                "name": "asset_values",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "投资组合中每个资产的价值"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "risk_level",
                "description": "返回投资组合的风险水平"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TaxOptimization.suggest",
        "description": "提供税务优化策略的建议",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "income",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "年收入"
            },
            {
                "name": "deductions",
                "type": "LIST",
                "description": "可用的税务扣除项"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "strategies",
                "description": "返回税务优化策略的建议"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
